## Visual

A tall, ornate, dark navy and gold infographic poster is arranged as eight numbered panels in a two-column grid, with a header, series arc, and concluding thesis band. Diagrams use sacred-geometry circles, trees, brains, arrows, feedback loops, and triadic systems to connect theological language with computational learning concepts. The style evokes illuminated manuscripts, medieval cosmology, and technical systems diagrams, with serif small-caps typography, fine gold borders, teal highlights, and red-orange accents for pain, error, and suffering.
